parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I’m sorry, Miss Bhatt. I was just researching on the internet…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We got a call from Eve Cathedral.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.The priest suspects someone is trying to rob them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Someone trying to steal from a church? What evidence do we have to go on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlEx.The priest heard something last night and this morning we got the call.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It’s just… How is this a case?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I can head over there… but it’s looking stormy outside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.Take the case, 1Hero. I’m not arguing with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.What about David? He hasn’t left the office in weeks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I’m heading over to the Wilkes Mansion later this afternoon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Deal with the church and then we can talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I thought you said the case was closed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.There’s some loose ends to tie up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Do you think Charles Wilkes was murdered?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Go to Eve Cathedral. We’ll talk later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.If I finish early, I’m coming to the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Don’t rush your work. I can handle the Wilkes case without your help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.But I might be able to pick the lock with the right tool.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Maybe I can use my lock pick to open it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.What do you need, 1Hero? Looking for something to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.If you’re going to speak with Lillian Wilkes, do it sooner rather than later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Go to your meeting, 1Hero. And don’t do anything stupid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.David’s been sent to the mansion. Don’t be late for your interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.When you get back, I want to meet with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDeNo1.What the hell do you think you’re doing!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Sorry, Melissa… Erica and I have become… close.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeMaAgNo1.You think that gives you free reign over the interrogation room for your sex antics?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.You should be fired and if it wasn’t for your arrangement with Kimura, you’d already be out the door.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Well then I guess it’s good I went out of my way to make something happen in this department for a change.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeMaOp.Is that what you think? You think we sit around twiddling our thumbs because we don’t bite on every coincidence?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.How many times were you wrong before you finally hit on something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.You have no idea what you’re doing. You’ve never been told no in your whole life.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.If all I have keeping me here is Kimura, then I don’t need to impress you anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.You keep that tongue of yours under control.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.You’ve put all your eggs in that basket of hers and now you better put your money where your mouth is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMaOp^.Fuck this. She has her head so far up her own ass she can’t see what Andrea sees in me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.I’m not just a pretty face. I’m a damn good detective and I know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe.Showing your face at the office again?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoOp.Does Andrea know you were at the mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.No… My meeting with Duncan was top secret.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I… I don’t know… But I’m still alive.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m going to look for Duncan’s goon. See what you can dig up on Vayne Stone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe.You know how I get when you start ordering me around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Hey! You spy on me plenty. You’ve been gunning for me ever since I started here!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Unless you’re a carpet muncher, it’s exactly what I think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Listen here, 1Hero. Perhaps you and I are not that different.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Clearly, if you’re willing to finger yourself in the office.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Unless you want to lose your job, not a word of this to anyone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.Are you kidding me? I’m not telling a soul…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.But… what you did was way worse than what I did.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeShClNo1.What!? You literally came all over a woman in the interrogation room!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.And you’re twiddling your bean to a subordinate!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I saw the whole thing! You can’t lie!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp^.This is priceless. She’s been a thorn in my side for a long time now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.But the thought of Melissa thinking about me… sexually…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.No… No way. I’m not going to fuck my boss.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe^.But… Would I, if she wanted to?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.To say I’m disappointed would be an understatement.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Had I known there was an undercover operation taking place, I’d have kept my distance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.1Hero, what the hell do you think you’re doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s more to this than just the Eclipse Guild…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.We’re on the verge of taking down the Guild. It’s imperative that the operation remains hidden…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Do you have any idea what would happen if Nellie gets caught?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.What if an innocent person gets killed?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.There are officers posted at the mansion. Perhaps we could do the same for the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Questions are already rising about the lack of search efforts in the forest…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.No one has to know about the secret basement in the church. We just need someone watching it to make sure things are safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.I’m pulling officers from the mansion. I can reassign one person to keep watch of the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp^.Yes, Miss Kimura. I think that’ll be fine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.1Hero, I want you to show the officer the church, but do not mention this secret basement.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Just how far into the cave does the Guild bunker reach?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Stop asking questions, 1Hero. This isn’t your operation…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I’m just worried… I know someone who lives very near the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.The Guild is not looking to harm civilians.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.The best advice I can give to you and your friends is to stay away… stay far away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Why the hell did you tell her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.I’m not risking my job so you can play hero for a case that’s not yours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.Go to the church. Don’t be late.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.Show some professionalism. What’s wrong with you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s got a lot of artwork in her house… She’s still keeping that stolen Rembrandt in her house...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Why not keep it at the station?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I stumbled into a room in her house… It had countless artifacts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I think she’s been working with the Guild for a long, long time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.As well as being the police commissioner? You think that’s possible?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Duncan Helmer told me her name is Vayne.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.I’ve heard that name before. Wasn’t there a Vayne Stone connected to Charles Wilkes in his hidden file?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Can you see what you can find?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Not here… It’ll be traced back to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We have Andrea’s USB drive… Can you do it from your house?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Yeah… I think I can do it without getting tracked.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m going to look for Duncan’s goon. See what you can dig up on Vayne Stone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe.You know how I get when you start ordering me around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.That goon is not going back to Duncan, but he is probably looking to get a fake passport.");
